## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not encompass all possible strategies for enhancing children's emotional intelligence. Additionally, the effectiveness of these strategies can vary depending on individual child characteristics and environmental factors. Further empirical research could provide more comprehensive insights into the long-term impacts of these practices.

